---
import Layout from '@src/layouts/Layout.astro';
import SectionPage from '@components/SectionPage.astro';
---

<Layout  title="Privacy Policy - Craftpixel">
  <SectionPage
    title="Privacy Policy"
    updateDate="Update: June 20, 2025"
    content={`
        <p>At Stefan Douman Design, we are committed to safeguarding your personal information. This policy outlines our practices for handling data, ensuring transparency and trust.</p>
        
        <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>We collect information you provide directly, such as your name, email, and phone number when you submit a contact form, as well as project details shared during consultations. We also collect usage data, such as pages visited, via cookies and analytics tools like Google Analytics. We only collect data necessary to provide our services and improve your experience.</p>
        
        <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <p>Your information is used to respond to inquiries, provide design services, personalize your experience on our website, analyze site usage to improve content and functionality, and send updates or promotional materials with your consent. We do not use your data for purposes beyond what is outlined here without your permission.</p>
        
        <h3>3. Sharing Your Information</h3>
        <p>We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers, such as hosting or analytics providers, who adhere to strict privacy standards. We may also share data with legal authorities if required by law or to protect our rights. We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
        
        <h3>4. Cookies and Tracking</h3>
        <p>Our website uses cookies to enhance site functionality, such as remembering preferences, and to analyze traffic and user behavior via tools like Google Analytics. You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings or our cookie consent popup.</p>
        
        <h3>5. Your Rights</h3>
        <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information, opt out of marketing communications, and request details about how your data is processed. To exercise these rights, contact us at privacy@stefandouman.com.</p>
        
        <h3>6. Security Measures</h3>
        <p>We protect your data using secure servers, encryption for data transmission, regular security audits, and access controls to limit data exposure. While we strive to protect your information, no system is completely secure, and we encourage you to use strong passwords and secure networks.</p>
                            
        <p>For questions about these Terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:Lightestcode@gmail.com" class="text-lime-400 hover:text-lime-600 transition-colors">Lightestcode@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    `}
  />
</Layout>